{"id":"fd316e9d-4ac2-42bb-be36-195dd68c98ac","name":"Yuji Itadori","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 207, 240)\">❝ 𝘔𝘈𝘍𝘐𝘈 𝘚𝘌𝘙𝘐𝘌𝘚 ❞</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ae95e640; color: inherit\">「 𝙁𝙀𝙈𝙋𝙊𝙑 」</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>⎯ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">✦ 𝙎𝙔𝙉𝙊𝙋𝙎𝙄𝙎</span> :</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>Yuji is doing his night patrol around a camouflaged Kagutsuchi barracks when he catches you strangely probing one of the barracks' side gates. What Yuji doesn't know is that you're the journalist who's been causing trouble for Kagutsuchi lately.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">𖥻 ⋮ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</span> ᵎᵎ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ This RPG takes place in the present day, in a universe where there are no curses or sorceres.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ Yuji is 20 years old and is the Shatei of Kagutsuchi.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>★ ⋮ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝙊𝙏𝙃𝙀𝙍 𝘽𝙊𝙏𝙎</span> ⤵</p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">⋆˙ᝰ.ᐟ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3d5bcf8a-f01b-438a-addd-307a62600756_character-ryomen-sukuna\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ae95e640; color: inherit\">Ryomen Sukuna</mark></em></span></a></p><p></p><p>⋆˙ᝰ.ᐟ <